snippet.title: Dakota Johnson Reveals Amber Should Be Cancelled and Not Johnny Depp
snippet.description:
Dakota Johnson Reveals Her Anger That Johnny And Not Amber Is Being Cancelled 
Actress and model: Dakota Johnson has expressed her anger towards the anti-Johnny Depp notion that is gaining popularity on social media right now. Dakota is best known for appearing in the popular film Fifty Shades and is also the daughter of Don Johnson and Melanie Griffith. 
Dakota's comments come at a time when Johnny Depp has been gaining significant ground in his legal battle against Amber Heard. However, the actor has also already been fired from all his projects, including Pirates of the Caribbean. It turns out that this is exactly what Dakota Johnson had to say as well. So, how has she expressed her anger against Amber Heard? Let's find out that and much more in this video.
